    h4.mt-4#media-order
      +extLink("https://getbootstrap.com/docs/4.1/layout/media-object/#order") Order
    p.my-2 (1) Change DOM element order: move 
      code img
      |  to the last
    div.media.mt-2
      div.media-body
        +bodyTextExample
      img.ml-3.order-last(src="../img/48x48.svg" alt="48x48 placeholder image")
    p.mt-4.mb-2 (2) Change order with 
      code .order-*
      |  of 
      a(href="utilities-3.html#flex") Flex utilities
      |  .
    div.media.mt-2
      img.ml-3.order-last(src="../img/48x48.svg" alt="48x48 placeholder image")
      div.media-body
        +bodyTextExample
    h4.mt-4#media-list
      +extLink("https://getbootstrap.com/docs/4.1/layout/media-object/#media-list") Media list
    p.my-2 Example using 
      code ul
      |  (same as 
      code ol
      |  )
    ul.list-unstyled
      each n in [1,2,3]
        li.media.my-3
          +imageSample
          div.media-body
            h5.mt-0= `Media heading (${n})`
            | Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. 
    ul.struct.mt-3
      li
        code ul.list-unstyled
        ul
          li.cls Remove prefix symbols with 
            code .list-unstyled
            |  (⇒ 
            a(href="content-1.html#typo-list-unstyled") Lists - Unstyled
            |  )
          li Items 
            code li.media.my-3
            ul
              li.cls Adjust top/bottom margins with 
                code .my-3
                |  (⇒ 
                a(href="utilities-4.html#spacing") Spacing utilities
                |  )
              li See 
                a(href="#media-example") Basic example
                |  for inside
    h2.mt-5#utilities
      +extLink("https://getbootstrap.com/docs/4.1/layout/utilities-for-layout/") Utilities for layout
    ul.mb-3
      li Showing/Hiding elements ⇒ 
        a(href="utilities-2.html#display") Display
      li Layout using flexbox ⇒ 
        a(href="utilities-3.html#flex") Flex
      li Setting margins and/or paddings ⇒ 
        a(href="utilities-4.html#spacing") Spacing
      li Showing/Hiding elements without changing layout ⇒ 
        a(href="utilities-5.html#visibility") Visibility

    +breadcrumbLevel1("Layout(2): Media object/Utilities for layout")
